WHAT IS VIBE CODING?
AI assisted coding based on intuition rather than understanding.

AGI(ARTIFICIAL GENERAL INTELLIGENCE)- It is a theoretical concept in AI where a machine possesses the ability to understand, learn, and apply its intelligence to any intellectual task that a human being can.

